HS Comparison Report for Bowen High School


About This Report

This is a demonstration of an interactive report that can be produced with custom content in interactive elements.

This report is generated with the open source R programming language, and the specific code for generating this report is accessible in open source at this link. In addition to offering transparency, having code in open source invites collaborators to comment and contribute, regardless of institutional affiliation.

These data represent statistics from the 2018-19 School Year, sourced at this link from the City of Chicago Data Portal.
